ZAP is a derivative work: a brand-neutral fork of libcapnp that keeps the wire
model and KJ support library while adding the whitespace-significant `.zap`
schema grammar (the offside rule, no braces, auto-assigned field ordinals) and
the `zap` schema compiler binary that every language plugin executes.
